text.0: A Trump campaign ad uses an out-of-context video clip to claim Biden admitted he will come for the guns of Americans if he’s elected. In the unedited video, Biden was talking about his opposition to so-called “assault weapons” — not all firearms. https://t.co/0L1MrNW2hn #FactCHAT
